            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": ". Naturally, that makes some people sad, those who hate McLaren with a passion joyous, and well-heeled collectors eager.",
            "type": "text",
